{"tid":1220033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳智思：政府沒開會「是緩衝下」","createTime":"2019-06-14T02:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T07:38:37.000Z","uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"679d9343f49e3816cf0532b89005a664aa94542b","tid":1220033,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:22:55.000Z","msg":"反對修訂《逃犯條例》示威周三（12日）釀成嚴重衝突，行政會議召集人陳智思今早（14日）在港台節目表示，此刻在對立及激烈的情況下，要就修例作討論難度很高。<br />\n<br />\n陳智思稱，特首林鄭月娥承諾任期內有很多事會做，不只是一個議題，很多事也要考慮、要盤算。他留意到政府這兩天沒有開會，「估計是緩衝下先，重新看究竟這個法案市民是否知道是什麼事」。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否要有人問責，陳智思承認，自己亦低估了修例的反響，包括商界，「有很多恐懼消息不斷出了街」，他需否問責則交由特首決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190614/s00001/1560477102338/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%A8%B1%E5%B0%8D%E7%AB%8B%E6%BF%80%E7%83%88%E4%B8%8B%E9%9B%A3%E8%AB%96%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E9%99%B3%E6%99%BA%E6%80%9D-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B2%92%E9%96%8B%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%B7%A9%E8%A1%9D%E4%B8%8B%E3%80%8D?fbclid=IwAR0lPvvLvmH_LDeVRXww-Kcxua8b56a14ENYol8T3o6TTDGmln7nWCuX3Kk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190614%2Fs00001%2F1560477102338%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25BF%2580%25E7%2583%2588%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%259B%25A3%25E8%25AB%2596%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%2599%25BA%25E6%2580%259D-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%25B2%2592%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E8%25A1%259D%25E4%25B8%258B%25E3%2580%258D%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0lPvvLvmH_LDeVRXww-Kcxua8b56a14ENYol8T3o6TTDGmln7nWCuX3Kk&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=6340842d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190614%2Fs00001%2F1560477102338%2F%25E3%2580%2